    <h1 class="opener__hed  -is-over-bg opener__hed--light opener__hed--small" >        Inside the Historic Suit That the Gun Industry and Republicans Are on the Verge of Killing
    </h1>

    
            <div class="article-meta-1  -is-over-bg article-meta-1--light">
            <span class="article-meta-1__byline">
                by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/vernal-coleman">Vernal Coleman</a>            </span>
            <time class="article-meta-1__pubdate">
                <time class="timestamp" datetime="2024-03-27EDT05:00">March 27, 5 a.m. EDT</time>
            </time>
        </div>
    
    </div> <!-- Close .opener__topic-title-dek-wrapper -->

        <div class="content"> <!-- not sure if this is the best way to reestablish the text column -->
        <h2 class="opener__dek opener__dek--match-text-column" >            For 25 years, gunmakers have repeatedly tried to end one city’s lawsuit over illegal gun sales. Meanwhile, illicit purchases of firearms continued at an unrelenting and hazardous pace.
        </h2>
    </div>
    
</div>
        
<div class="article-meta-1
     article-meta-1--left      article-meta-1--hide-byline " data-pp-location="article meta">

    <span class="article-meta-1__byline" data-pp-location="article byine">
