    <div class="story-card__description">
                        <a class="story-card__series" href="https://www.propublica.org/series/uprooted">Uprooted</a>
        
        <h3 class="story-card__hed" >
            <a href="https://www.propublica.org/article/uprooted-documentary-christopher-newport-university-black-neighborhoods">
                                    “Uprooted” Explores How University Expansion and Eminent Domain Led to Black Land Loss
                            </a>
        </h3>

        <p class="story-card__dek" >
                            Watch this examination of a Black community’s decadeslong battle to hold onto their land as city officials wielded eminent domain.
                    </p>

        <p class="story-card__byline">
            by <span class="name">Brandi Kellam</span>, <span class="name">Christopher Tyree</span> and <span class="name">Louis Hansen</span>, <a href="https://vcij.org/">Virginia Center for Investigative Journalism at WHRO</a>, and <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/lisa-riordan-seville">Lisa Riordan Seville</a> and <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/mauricio-rodriguez-pons">Mauricio Rodríguez Pons</a>, ProPublica,             <time class="timestamp" datetime="2023-12-09EST06:00">Dec. 9, 2023, 6 a.m. EST</time>
        </p>

